408
00:24:29,438 --> 00:24:31,338
The Gunma Prefectural Police arrive in the next episode.

409
00:24:31,338 --> 00:24:32,438
It's Inspector Yamamura.

410
00:24:32,438 --> 00:24:34,138
-Bummers! -We've got to solve the case quickly.

